00:17:43,540 --> 00:17:47,580
 But if he came back, that joy would be ridiculous.

438
00:17:47,580 --> 00:17:50,700
 And I would not stop at saying, "You're forgiven, son.

439
00:17:50,700 --> 00:17:51,540
 "Now go do your thing.

440
00:17:51,540 --> 00:17:52,860
 "You're forgiven, come be a servant."

