00:17:52,860 --> 00:17:54,820
 No, I would throw my arms around him,

442
00:17:54,820 --> 00:17:58,820
 'cause he's my boy, 'cause he's my kid, he's me.

443
00:17:58,820 --> 00:18:01,140
 Right, and I think if you understand this story,

444
00:18:01,140 --> 00:18:03,100
 and you understand the power of family,

445
00:18:03,100 --> 00:18:04,660
 that's what Jesus is talking about.

446
00:18:04,660 --> 00:18:07,180
 It's not just about the forgiveness of the sin,

447
00:18:07,180 --> 00:18:10,660
 it's about the ultimate goal being restoring us

448
00:18:10,660 --> 00:18:12,420
 into the right identity.

449
00:18:12,420 --> 00:18:15,020
 The scriptures talk about this all over the place.

450
00:18:15,020 --> 00:18:17,900
 Why do you think it is that we're called sons and daughters

451
00:18:17,900 --> 00:18:19,420
 of God, children of God?

