00:18:37,840 --> 00:18:38,980
 make sure we don't sin too much,

462
00:18:38,980 --> 00:18:40,260
 like go through all these rituals.

463
00:18:40,260 --> 00:18:44,660
 He says, "When you pray, pray like this."

464
00:18:44,660 --> 00:18:47,860
 Our father, relationship.

