00:19:57,820 --> 00:19:59,200
 All right, some of you don't have to try that hard.

495
00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:01,200
 It's pretty easy for some.

496
00:20:01,200 --> 00:20:04,200
 But not with my kid, not with my family.

497
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:06,560
 And God has this posture towards us.

498
00:20:06,560 --> 00:20:08,700
 That's why the ultimate blessing,

499
00:20:08,700 --> 00:20:11,200
 the ultimate thing we can receive is not a gift,

500
00:20:11,200 --> 00:20:12,860
 a Ferrari or a better job

501
00:20:12,860 --> 00:20:14,720
 or a more stable relationship at home.

502
00:20:14,720 --> 00:20:16,200
 The ultimate gift we can get

