00:20:17,960 --> 00:20:19,300
 That's what Emma was talking about.

505
00:20:19,300 --> 00:20:22,500
 By the blood of Jesus, we're not just forgiven,

506
00:20:22,500 --> 00:20:24,620
 we're brought into his family.

507
00:20:24,620 --> 00:20:28,620
 This is how God intended humanity to be,

508
00:20:28,620 --> 00:20:32,160
 in relationship with him, heirs of his,

509
00:20:32,160 --> 00:20:36,100
 made to be like him, protected by him, his children.

510
00:20:36,100 --> 00:20:37,740
 This is why Jesus in John three

511
00:20:37,740 --> 00:20:40,240
 would speak to Nicodemus at night and he would say,

512
00:20:40,240 --> 00:20:46,000
 "You must be, you must be born again.

513
00:20:46,000 --> 00:20:48,340
 "You must be born into this family

514
00:20:48,340 --> 00:20:50,060
 "because if you are in this family,

515
00:20:50,060 --> 00:20:52,140
 "there is no sin that is deep enough

